Not currently, we will be adding support for more models in the future.

Currently supported models are Mobilenets, Inception V3 and Smart Reply.
Please look at the list of supported models here. 
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/lite/g3doc/models.md
